==Line of succession ==
The [[line of succession]] regarding who would act as Secretary of Transportation in the event of a vacancy or incapacitation is as follows:&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web|url=http://nodis3.gsfc.nasa.gov/displayEO.cfm?id=EO_13485_|title=Executive Order 13485: Providing an Order of Succession Within the Department of Transportation|last=Obama, Barack|date=January 14, 2009|publisher=NASA Online Directives Information System|accessdate=January 2, 2010}}&lt;/ref&gt;

