==Living former secretaries of energy==
{{see also|List of living former members of the United States Cabinet}}
As of {{Monthyear}}, there are ten living former secretaries of energy, the oldest being [[Charles Duncan Jr.]] (served 1979–1981, born 1926). The most recent secretary of energy to die was [[Samuel Bodman]] (served 2005–2009, born 1938) on September 7, 2018. 
